  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ゲームパーティーでは、1つのカートリッジで5つの異なるゲームを楽しむことができます。含まれているゲームは、エアホッケー、ホッケー、ピンボール、バスケットボール、そしてマインド-Qです。友達を誘って、楽しいマルチプレイヤーゲームを始めましょう！",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Game Party is a game published by Coconuts Japan Entertainment Co., Ltd., which was released in Japan in 1990 for the Nintendo Famicom.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Game Party is a party video game developed by FarSight Studios and published by Midway. Game Party was retailed as a budget title for the Wii. It is the first game in the Game Party series. It was released on November 27, 2007, in North America; on February 14, 2008, in Australia; and in Europe on February 15, 2008.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
